Description:
The artisan tells you that he is ready to execute his craft, but since pure art only happens once, he will only work with the trinket of one of you.

He wants to know who among you is ready for the honor of wearing the final work of such a renowned artist.

When he is done, a piece of him will always accompany one of you!
DescriptionAction: Who is ready for such honor?
